      takeaway: "Size amplifies whatever it touches, so it gets raised like a salary. Fifty-plus logged trades of positive expectancy, A-grade process, and a survived losing streak open the gate, and the raise then comes in 25 to 50 percent steps. Drawdowns cut size automatically and immediately. Confidence is not a milestone, and neither is a hot week.",
